{"tid":1613842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭入一入嚟，做齊呢三樣，香港人同popo必定雙贏","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:51:58.000Z","uid":8477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e97f764a4b5e2012da43ab68b1cfb9f2e634cf","tid":1613842,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>第一：立即解散警隊</ins></strong><br />\n呢層唔洗多講，呢一刻就算你跪曬地同我地講成立獨立調查都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第二：被遣散警員直接加入解放軍</ins></strong><br />\n當然人工要跟返解放軍制度，可能你會問，得幾千蚊人工，到時班狗實發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放心，呢層幫你諗埋，既然班狗咁愛國，直接將佢地一家大細移送大灣區生活，你有你生活，我有我忙碌，各不相干自然無人唔滿意<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第三：解放軍全面接管香港保安</ins></strong><br />\n老老柒柒，而家同解放軍執法真係無咩分別，既然係咁直接給我一個痛快，好多香港人都期待俾全世界首屈一指軍事隊伍保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16b25d85f7531ac2b1c0b70a63142ea33b05aeb","tid":1613842,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"真焦土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23ac0fe9fd7f03ca5c7d47521be1cd96cf60451","tid":1613842,"uid":265133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"我焦土撑樓主 一齊食草"},{"pid":"cf9a8a5dc86a017379132ea93065be44488ea709","tid":1613842,"uid":8477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c23ac0fe9fd7f03ca5c7d47521be1cd96cf60451","tid":1613842,"uid":265133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"我焦土撑樓主 一齊食草"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"傻豬 大躍進都有肉食啦<br />\n諗起伯母條腿都流曬口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}